    topic: "Pharmacology",
    subtopic: "Inhaled corticosteroid adverse effects",
    stem: `A mother brings her 5-year-old boy to your practice for consultation. He has recently been started on FLixotide® (fluticasone propionate) inhaler, 4-hourly, after he was diagnosed with asthma. She wants to know about the adverse effects of this drug. Which one of the following is not an adverse effect of this medication?`,
